00:02:49.600 --> 00:02:53.180
cancer. And in particular, he's going to be covering targeting

50
00:02:53.260 --> 00:02:56.960
ARID1A mutation cancers with ARID1B degraders

51
00:02:57.640 --> 00:03:00.760
and also novel combinations for

52
