SMARCA2 inhibitors and SMARCA4

53
00:03:04.820 --> 00:03:08.420
mutation cancers. So without further ado, I want to

54
00:03:09.240 --> 00:03:12.240
introduce Mark O'Connor from AstraZeneca. Thanks for being here, Mark.

55
00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.120
Thanks.

56
00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:20.480
Just before Mark starts,

57
00:03:21.600 --> 00:03:23.940
please feel free to submit your questions.

58
00:03:24.760 --> 00:03:28.500
We will hold questions till the end, and we're going to have a

59
